{"data":[{"id":560404733,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560404733","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545835134,"updated_time":1545836613,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"disallowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我来说吧，我当年和你也是一样，不过我更早，我在初中就想这个问题。我想的更愚蠢：如果证明哥德巴赫猜想能不能保送进我们当地最好的高中？因为这个，我甚至有几天晚上不写作业思考这个问题，也耽误了不少精力。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e直到我上了高中，我才发现初中我学到的就是渣渣。推而广之也是一样的，你在高中或者竞赛中学的在整个数学体系中只是冰山一角。我说的题主你明白吗？评论里说的那些数学专著你可以看一下，如果真的能看懂，也许你是对的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我很想用亲身想法让你知道，天才真的特别少特别少，少到我们都不是。我很庆幸当时我知道的太少没有“成功”证明，也希望你能正视这个现实。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e高斯曾经是我的目标，因为他高中时证明了世界难题。但是，不一样的是，他家庭就是数学世家，从小就开始学习数学。你真的有这样的条件吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果我上面的问题你回答否，那请取消吧，这个事只会成为一个段子。如果你的证明真的得到认可，我也会为你喝彩。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-------------------------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再加一点吧，我当时和那个匿名自称老师说的一样，有想法，但是成绩不好。如果真的想找一个方法考上好大学，最好另辟蹊径，或许你拥有足够的能力可以证明一个简单的猜想。\u003cb\u003e但是\u003c/b\u003e如果你想找考上好大学的\u003cb\u003e捷径\u003c/b\u003e，我建议你打消这个念头，好好学习才是最终出路。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我来说吧，我当年和你也是一样，不过我更早，我在初中就想这个问题。我想的更愚蠢：如果证明哥德巴赫猜想能不能保送进我们当地最好的高中？因为这个，我甚至有几天晚上不写作业思考这个问题，也耽误了不少精力。直到我上了高中，我才发现初中我学到的就是渣…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=698\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3